           <h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap"><a data-tip="p$t$wen-zhao-69" href="/people/wen-zhao-69">文召</a>,<strong title="游走于互联网与金融" class="zu-question-my-bio">游走于互联网与金融</strong></h3>
           <a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
          </div>
          <div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="36">
           <span class="voters"><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhang-shen-hua-60" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-shen-hua-60" class="zg-link" title="张珅华">张珅华</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yu-mi-35-71" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yu-mi-35-71" class="zg-link" title="鱼米">鱼米</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$cheng-yan-81-89" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/cheng-yan-81-89" class="zg-link" title="程岩">程岩</a></span></span>
