           <h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap"><a data-tip="p$t$dan-diao-han-shu" href="/people/dan-diao-han-shu">单调喊数</a>,<strong title="青春就是过自己想要的生活。。。" class="zu-question-my-bio">青春就是过自己想要的生活。。。</strong></h3>
           <a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
          </div>
          <div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="284">
           <span class="voters"><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$cathy-jiang-29" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/cathy-jiang-29" class="zg-link" title="Cathy Jiang">Cathy Jiang</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yu-bai-51-48" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yu-bai-51-48" class="zg-link" title="从此醉">从此醉</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户</span></span>
